# Project Structure

```
src/
  config/        → third-party wiring & cross-cutting (env, prisma, exception filters)
  features/      → feature modules (1 folder per domain resource)
  helpers/        → shared pure utilities (no @Module / @Controller)
prisma/
  schema.prisma  → single source of truth for DB models
  migrations/    → Prisma migrations
  seed.ts        → database seeder
```

## Rules

- Fitur baru selalu di `src/features/<feature-name>/`
- Config/infra third-party di `src/config/<nama-config>/`
- Pure utility/helper di `src/helpers/`
- Jangan taruh business logic di `src/config/` atau `src/helpers/`

## Naming

- File: `kebab-case` → `create-user.dto.ts`, `users.controller.ts`
- Class: `PascalCase` → `UsersService`, `CreateUserDto`
- Route prefix: plural resource → `@Controller('users')`

## Imports

- Relative import dalam satu feature: `./users.service`
- Cross-feature/config: absolute dari root → `src/config/prisma/prisma.service`
- Prisma client: `@prisma/generated/client`
